{"tid":94123,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)基友奸獄 夜刑者 危機解密","createTime":"2017-01-25T03:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T08:24:03.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5bb8e0620ec23849b9a996af887f23a162c0972","tid":94123,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T03:39:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=M1cunQxZFzHJAHuAEZ8SVmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=048d8c5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=M1cunQxZFzHJAHuAEZ8SVmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=92b2c1c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/52/Big_Stan_Poster.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F5%2F52%2FBig_Stan_Poster.png&h=a96a9edd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/allen201242002/1380454896-2040006459_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fallen201242002%2F1380454896-2040006459_n.jpg&h=d3211152&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e5/Source_Code_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe5%2FSource_Code_Poster.jpg&h=fc720eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.居住在洛杉磯的斯坦&middot;明頓（羅伯&middot;施奈德Rob Schneider飾）是一名巧舌如簧，事業有成的房地產商人。他張狂無度，滿嘴大話，最終不可避免地捲入一場 案，面臨著為期3年的牢獄之災，而他所去的正是一所臭名昭著，以暴力著稱的監獄。不過在此之前，斯坦還有6個月的自由時間。本來心情無比煩躁，還 和女友敏迪（珍妮弗&middot;莫瑞森Jennifer Morrison飾）鬧出不快。為了防止在獄中被人強暴，斯坦開始拜師訪友，修煉武功，期間更得到一名神秘武師（大衛&middot;卡拉丁 的指導...<br />\n<br />\n2.喬伊(傑森史坦森 飾)，是前特種部隊成員，自從軍事法庭逃亡後，輾轉流落街頭；因緣際會下他獲得了一個新的身分，並開始了他的新生活。此外，一位幫派份子也相中他的&ldquo;天賦&rdquo;而給了他一個賺大錢的新工作。但是，儘管如此，過去卻無法與他分割，他開始幫助那些過去和他一起流落街頭的同伴，並開始尋找失聯許久的戀人。殊不知，這一切就在他發現自己曾摯愛的人遭到殺害時，一切都變了調；為了找出殺人兇手，他開始晝伏夜出，化身為神出鬼沒的黑夜制裁者且以牙還牙的復仇天使..<br />\n<br />\n3.寇特&middot;史蒂文斯上尉（傑克&middot;葛倫霍飾）本是美國陸軍直昇機飛行員，某一日他發現自己變成了一個高中歷史教師蕭恩，與蕭恩曖昧中的女伴克莉絲汀娜&middot;華倫（蜜雪兒&middot;摩納漢飾）一同搭火車前往芝加哥，正當他感到丈二金剛摸不著頭緒的時候，火車爆炸了，他又回到一個軍事基地，接受柯琳&middot;古德溫上尉（薇拉&middot;法蜜嘉飾）的模擬測試，寇特被告知，他被五角大廈選中，進入了拉利奇博士（傑弗瑞&middot;萊特飾）發明的「原始碼系統」調查過去發生過的恐怖攻擊案件..<br />\n<br />\n12 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6ee43e91b219050d46697cb529ccc3d1c71481","tid":94123,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d85d06d101375d9f888edaca42c2e46772f4d2d","tid":94123,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d9bdcdc86b0fa758f2cfcb0ac68e216e0ccdf6","tid":94123,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bcd90d19f1f864f5059608e844cd6da11511ec","tid":94123,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939f1bbaf818caf346cfa4f890847a55dee31c7c","tid":94123,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87874219cd8a1222318087f4de703542418d2ef3","tid":94123,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9fac9d2d5ecff840589edce21969a60f7ffd72","tid":94123,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c687451895a97d9ef78be643175bb3c04db718","tid":94123,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdd84895ad0fd8331a204fa5a0ebdd2299f07a8","tid":94123,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}